content: Very informative and featuring great tips and advice. Recommended.
Informative and very simple too follow.
Recently discovered I'm a diabetic thru hereditary and that bums me out cos I'm not a sweet tooth kinda person. Thank you so much for this wonderful app.
Very refreshing and informative read. Would help everyone not just diabetics.

For those of us with diabetes(found out on my 30th b-day, I'm now almost 60) we can always use ALL the help we can get. And this app is a wonderful place to find information. I'm using the add free version and just using this with DELIGHT. A well spent .99 cent. So come on and dive right in and find stuff that can help you AND MAYBE EVEN HELP SAVE YOUR LIFE. Gr8 app everyone. God bless us all.
